autoscope.utils

Annotation Type AutoscopeRunOptions


  • @Inherited
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface AutoscopeRunOptions
    Used to switch between Autoscope driver, virtual devices, simulators, and test environment. For debug use only. Add the @AutoscopeRunOptions() annotation above any test method to change how that test will be run Be sure to remove any occurrences of @AutoscopeRunOptions from test classes before pushing to GitHub
